question: Which restaurant can I find along the route to Centennial High School Football Stadium, Roswell, GA within 80 kilometers from Mountain Park, Lilburn, GA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-84.118544 33.847394)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-84.292979 34.007322)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-84.118544 33.847394)',4326)::geography, 80000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-84.118544 33.847394)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
